data.description:
Phenomenal large all brick ranch with 2 main level bedrooms backing up to main St in columbia on nice private street. Home has nice updates and ready for new owners. Beautiful wood floors throughout main level. Has massive living room with gas fireplace. Leads in to over sized eat in kitchen with updated cabinetry and appliances. This home has so much potential with large private wooded back yard and a full open water proofed basement from woods waterproofing. Breezeway could main level laundry or buyer can decorate
(Paint and flooring) as they choose. Has covered back concrete patio and over sized garage. Home has been very well maintained. Occupancy inspection will be completed asap and Seller is providing home warranty from Americas Preferred ($ 565.00 value). Schedule your showing as this one will not last long.
